name: Healing System
description:
【English】Nice to meet you all. NFT art was exhibited for the first time.
I really created it because I want to contribute to creating the ideal digital space.

It will be better and perfect from next time, so I would be happy if you can buy it this time and show off about me to people around me.
I'm collecting military funds to work as an artist, so I really, really do my best, so thank you.

【China】很高兴见到你。 我们第一次展出了NFT艺术。
我想为创造理想的数字空间做出贡献，所以我认真地创造了它。

从下一次开始，我会变得更完美，所以我很高兴，如果我买它，并吹嘘我周围的人。
我真的很努力，因为我正在收集军事资金，作为一个艺术家工作，谢谢。

【Japan】初めまして、宜しくお願い致します。

【Thailand】
Is deas bualadh leat go léir. Chruthaigh mé i ndáiríre é. Ceannaigh é le do thoil.
